briefdescription.para: This file is backported from cereal 1.3 to support the serialization of objects of type associative containers (std::map, std::pair, etc.)

detaileddescription.para: This file add the support for serialization of containers for any version of cereal starting from 1.1.2 that is required by Ubuntu 16.04
Support for the PairAssociativeContainer refinement of the AssociativeContainer concept.
